comments: Williams (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Hachimura's (WAS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Wagner (WAS) legally contests Batum's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) makes marginal contact with Westbrook (WAS) as he secures the rebound.
Williams (LAC) makes marginal contact with Westbrook's (WAS) arm at the end of the drive as he prepares to pass.
Ibaka (LAC) makes marginal contact with Wagner's (WAS) arm after the release of his jump shot that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Beverly (LAC)  makes contact to Bertans' (WAS) body and affects his SQBR when both reach for the loose ball.
Bertans (WAS) legally contests Batum's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (WAS) and Ibaka (LAC) engage and disengage with each other during the rebound.
Mann (LAC) touches the ball before it reaches its apex.
Wagner (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Beverley's (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Beverley (LAC) cleanly blocks Beal's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
Leonard's (LAC) off-arm makes contact with Beal's (WAS) face at the start of the drive.
Beverley (LAC) commits a take foul on Westbrook (WAS).
Batum (LAC) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Hachimura (WAS).
Bertans (WAS) legally contests Batum's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) commits a take foul on Westbrook (WAS).
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Hachimura's (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Beal (WAS) makes contact with Batum's (LAC) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Mann (LAC) commits a take foul on Westbrook (WAS).
Hachimura (WAS) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) places a hand on Beal's (WAS) side as he is dribbling but the contact is marginal and he does not apply force to knock Beal out of bounds.
Williams (LAC) never has full possession of the ball as it is deflected from the font court to the back court.
Bertans (WAS) commits a take foul on Zubac (LAC).
Beverley (LAC) commits a take foul on Hachimura (WAS).
Westbrook (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball and taps the rebound away from Zubac (LAC).
